---
layout: layout.njk
permalink: "/years/"
title: Browse by Year
description: Browse Risen Word Easter poems by contest year.
---

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
  <h1 class="font-playfair text-4xl font-bold text-center text-text mb-2">Browse by Year</h1>
  <p class="text-center text-gray-500 mb-10">Each year, poets share their Easter reflections in our annual contest.</p>

  <ul class="space-y-4" role="list">
    {% for year in collections.contestYears | reverse %}
      {% set count = collections.poemsByYear[year] | length %}
      {% set contest = collections.contestsByYear[year] %}
      <li>
        <a
          href="/years/{{ year | slugify }}/"
          class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 rounded-2xl border border-[#e8e4dd] bg-white hover:border-accent hover:shadow-lg transition-all group"
        >
          <div>
            <span class="font-playfair text-2xl font-bold text-text group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">{{ year }}</span>
            {% if contest and contest.theme %}
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1 italic">Theme: &#8220;{{ contest.theme }}&#8221;</p>
            {% endif %}
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">{{ count }} poem{% if count != 1 %}s{% endif %}</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-accent text-sm font-semibold opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" aria-hidden="true">Browse →</span>
        </a>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</div>
